G","value":"false"},{"id":"AnillosDeCompromiso","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"ReferenciaDeLujo","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"ReferenciaMadre","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"VentaSinStock","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"SenyalInternet","type":"FLAG","value":"false"},{"id":"SenyalInternetCodificacion","type":"FLAG","value":"true"}]},{"id":"ProveedorMarca","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"NumeroProveedor","type":"STRING","value":"0189472"},{"id":"NombreProveedor","type":"STRING","value":"MARQUES DE MURRIETA, S.A."},{"id":"Fabricante","type":"STRING","value":"0189472"},{"id":"DescripcionFabricante","type":"STRING","value":"MARQUES DE MURRIETA, S.A."},{"id":"Marca","type":"STRING","value":"MURRIETA"},{"id":"MarcaMostradaEnWeb","type":"RELATIONSHIP","groupID":"391","id_Ext":"2449511056","value":"MARQUES DE MURRIETA"}]},{"id":"DescripcionCorta","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"DescripcionTicket","type":"STRING","value":"VINO TINTO LA"}]},{"id":"DescripcionLargaDelProducto","ocurrence":0,"type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"DescripcionPrincipal","type":"STRING","children":[{"id":"es_ES","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"De color cereza intenso, brillante, borde granate y capa alta. En nariz recuerda ecos de fruta roja sana y madura en perfecta maduración, ciruela madura, notas especiadas (regaliz, vainillas), violeta, balsámicos que aportan mucha frescura, todo ello en un perfecto equilibrio con sutiles notas tostadas procedentes de su paso por barrica. En su paso por el paladar se muestra redondo, fino, de sutil opulencia, taninos amables bien envueltos, una acidez perfecta, buen juego de equilibrios, persistente y con un sabroso y largo final."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"With an intensely bright and deep cherry colour and maroon rim. The bouquet has echoes of perfectly ripe red fruits, ripe plum, spicy notes (liquorice, vanillas), violet and balsamics that add freshness, all in a perfect harmony with subtle toasted notes coming from its time in the barrel. Its mid-palate is rounded, fine, and of subtle opulence. It has well-covered, pleasant tannins, a perfect acidity, nice balance, and lingers with a full-flavoured, long finish."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Robe cerise intense, brillante, liseré grenat prononcé. Au nez, il affiche des rappels de fruits rouges sains et parfaitement mûrs, de la prune mûre, des notes épicées (réglisse, vanille), de la violette et des touches balsamiques qui lui donnent beaucoup de fraîcheur. L'ensemble est parfaitement équilibré avec de subtiles notes torréfiées issues du passage en barrique. Au palais, il est rond, fin, subtilement opulent, avec d'agréables tanins bien enveloppés, une acidité parfaite, un bon jeu d'équilibres et une fin de bouche persistante, longue et savoureuse."}]}]},{"id":"GestionComprasStock","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"Calificacion1","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion2","type":"STRING","value":"A"},{"id":"Calificacion4","type":"STRING","value":"2F"},{"id":"Calificacion5","type":"STRING","value":"2A"},{"id":"TipoDeGestion","type":"STRING","value":"06"}]},{"id":"DimensionesYPeso","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"UOM!Dimensiones!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"204","id_Ext":"347186090","value":"cm"},{"id":"UOM!PesoBruto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"206","id_Ext":"347187090","value":"g"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!VolumenContenidoNeto","type":"NUMBER","value":"0.0"},{"id":"UOM!VolumenContenidoNeto!Unidad","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"213","id_Ext":"347188090","value":"ml"},{"id":"PUM","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"EnlacePUM","type":"LOOKUP_TABLE","featureGroupID":"2530","id_Ext":"20552573090","value":"005"},{"id":"CantidadProducto","type":"NUMBER","value":"75.0"},{"id":"UnidadesProducto","type":"STRING","value":"001"}]}]},{"id":"ColoresYTallas","type":"GROUPING","children":[{"id":"ColorFabricante","type